                <h1>Essential Passport Photo Requirements: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>When taking a passport photo, ensure that it's in color and measures 2x2 inches. The background should be plain white or off-white. You must face the camera directly with a neutral expression, keeping both eyes open. Glasses are allowed but should not create glare. Head coverings for religious purposes are permitted, but facial features must be visible.</p>
